## Installation

```sh
pip install py-refacto
```

### Example Client Integration

##### Neovim

Until Refacto is not in the official nvim-lspconfig repository, you can use my fork [nymann/nvim-lspconfig](https://github.com/nymann/nvim-lspconfig/).

